   // Date handling Functions in RPGLE            
H                                                 
D MyDateISO       S               D   DatFmt(*ISO)
D MyDateUSA       S               D   DatFmt(*USA)
D MyDateEUR       S               D   DatFmt(*EUR)
D MyDateYMD       S               D   DatFmt(*YMD)
D MyDateMDY       S               D   DatFmt(*MDY)
D MyDateDMY       S               D   DatFmt(*DMY)
 /Free                                            
    MyDateISO = %date();                          
    MyDateUSA = MyDateISO;                        
    MyDateEUR = %date();                          
  //                                              
    MyDateYMD = MyDateISO;                        
    MyDateMDY = MyDateUSA;                        
    MyDateDMY = MyDateEUR;                        
    dsply       MyDateISO;                        
    dsply       MyDateUSA;                        
    dsply       MyDateEUR; 
         *Inlr = *on; 
 /End-free        
